{"tid":2009352,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［強國威水史］美國入口大陸KN95口罩60%+不合格，害死前線","createTime":"2020-05-09T16:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T17:19:29.000Z","uid":356907,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"25b8c01991717e307108f59e1058d10a1545b8fe","tid":2009352,"uid":356907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T16:29:55.000Z","msg":"5月7日，美国CDC国家职业安全与健康研究所（NIOSH）发布的最新检测发现，67 种不同类型的进口 N95 型口罩中，约有 60% 未达标。美国政府还强调，6成产品中又以从中国进口的KN95口罩（N95同等级）是&ldquo;重灾区&rdquo;。美国政府称，花大价钱买了中国口罩，反而却让一线医护人员陷入更大的感染风险中。美国 FDA表示，撤回中国60多家制造商向美国出口N95口罩的许可，将中国获准为美国生产N95口罩的制造商数量从大约80家减少到14家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/2R8bLNgowDd_Ov0_sMDNnw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2F2R8bLNgowDd_Ov0_sMDNnw&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpYGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=d409f112\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/2R8bLNgowDd_Ov0_sMDNnw</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思上面殘體字copy and paste 頂住先<br />\n<br />\n強國對人類又一貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e60e21d554ce4e55e94b9013f60d0743cd4504","tid":2009352,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T16:31:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f32fd9be582e61d229211e7b71d84588adf0e2d1","tid":2009352,"uid":356907,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"05e60e21d554ce4e55e94b9013f60d0743cd4504","tid":2009352,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T16:31:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T16:34:11.000Z","msg":"用電話整，慳時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa384a60697cecbf1899ff6e85e66c4c9db867f","tid":2009352,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />玩口罩外交玩到出神入化"},{"pid":"f48f23f203e13f75582fc24178ae650436e5272d","tid":2009352,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dis